<sect1 id="Filter.Degree">
	<title>Degree</title>
	<para>
		This filter allows users to filter out concepts that have a
		number of incoming / outgoing relations that is less than, equal or
		greater than the numbers set by the user in the filter window.
	</para>
	<para>
		<screenshot>
			<mediaobject>
				<imageobject>
